{"tid":1080903,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人睇Kolor Initialness Live 2019","createTime":"2019-03-28T02:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:08:29.000Z","uid":7275,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8eb491ae3ab7bed1932d7afe76097ea0728fe2","tid":1080903,"uid":7275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kALJjUD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkALJjUD.png&h=d984a7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTYCpma.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTYCpma.png&h=8e29b22c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKOLOR Initialness Live 2019<br />\n<br />\n記得自己的初衷嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得上次一起高歌的時候嗎？<br />\n記得我們的約會嗎？<br />\n這些我們一切都記得，記得在舞台上不留餘力地盡情演出，把瘋狂，熱血，搖滾，感性......一切的都抒發出來。<br />\n從不計較付出，只想給大家最好，<br />\n2019年，一齊締造回憶的一晚！<br />\n<br />\n大家久違了！Get ready！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地點：麥花臣場館 <br />\n時間：2019年7月26日<br />\n票價：$480/$380<br />\n購買$480觀眾人士可以用優惠價：<br />\n$200預訂限量Initialness相/譜*。<br />\n（*內容包括：新舊相集，歌曲創作背景/簡介和九首全樂器記錄樂譜）<br />\n<br />\n3月28號10:00am於KKTIX開售"},{"pid":"a35b95adeda1cb483e4c2d26d3a19699b12dbac8","tid":1080903,"uid":7275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"利申買咗四張地面企位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade23af0783000ae1b6e0eeb9126159e180ebc0b","tid":1080903,"uid":7275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:38:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361cd397dc1708126eaa81e59db74023a4655822","tid":1080903,"uid":169574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/fac